org.openehealth.ipf.commons.ihe.core.atna.custom

Class Hl7v3Auditor

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.openhealthtools.ihe.atna.auditor.IHEAuditor
      • org.openehealth.ipf.commons.ihe.core.atna.custom.Hl7v3Auditor

  • public class Hl7v3Auditor
extends org.openhealthtools.ihe.atna.auditor.IHEAuditor
    Implementation of HL7v3 Auditors to send audit messages for
    • ITI-44 (PIX v3)
    • ITI-45 (PIX v3)
    • ITI-46 (PIX v3)
    • ITI-47 (PDQ v3)
    • ITI-55 (XCPD)
    • ITI-56 (XCPD)
    • PCC-1 (QED)
    Author:
    Dmytro Rud
